            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pdp__banner-rubber">
        <div class="banner-rubber__content">
            <p class="banner-rubber__title">Rubber Hex Dumbbells</p>
            <p class="banner-rubber__description p">Again Faster® Rubber Hex Dumbbells offer one of the most effective ways to add variance to any training program. Functional dumbbell movements cultivate stability, coordination and strength in ways that cannot be achieved using a barbell. Lighter dumbbells are great tools for accommodating athletes with an injury or those not yet comfortable with a bar. Whether you are making your first equipment purchase or looking to expand your gym's capabilities, making dumbbells a priority will take your training to the next level.</p>
            <p class="banner-rubber__text">Need a way to organize your weights? Check out some of our Storage Options.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="banner-rubber__image--wrapper">
            <img class="pdp_img lazyload"
                    src="{{ section.settings.product_banner_image1.src | img_url: '620x720' }}"
                    data-src="{{ img_url }}"
                    data-widths="[540, 720, 900, 1080, 1296, 1512, 1728, 1944, 2048]"
                    data-aspectratio="{{ section.settings.product_banner_image1.aspect_ratio }}"
                    data-sizes="auto"
                    data-parent-fit="cover"
                    alt="{{ section.settings.product_banner_image1.alt | escape }}">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pdp__banner-description">
        <div class="banner-description__image--wrapper">
            <img class="pdp_img lazyload"
                    src="{{ section.settings.product_banner_image2.src | img_url: '620x720' }}"
                    data-src="{{ img_url }}"
                    data-widths="[540, 720, 900, 1080, 1296, 1512, 1728, 1944, 2048]"
                    data-aspectratio="{{ section.settings.product_banner_image2.aspect_ratio }}"
